api_list.name: /search/province/sector
api_list.description: finds the pdf files list for a given Canadian province code.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://hiei23-usw-app-v1.p.rapidapi.com/search/province/sector"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "hiei23-usw-app-v1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
